china buy u.s. hard and soft wheat privat export said china bought a total of 550,000 tonn of u.s. wheat under the export enhanc program , with final confirm by the u.s. depart of agricultur of the subsidi still await . the purcha consist of a total of 340,000 tonn of hard red winter wheat for variou may/aug shipment , with 210,000 tonn of soft red winter for aug/sept , the export said .